text.div:
This value set contains 3 concepts

MessageTransport

The protocol used for message transport

This value set defines its own terms in the system http://hl7.org/fhir/message-transport

CodeDisplayDefinition
http HttpThe application sends or receives messages using HTTP POST (may be over http or https).
ftp FtpThe application sends or receives messages using File Transfer Protocol.
mllp MllpThe application sends or receivers messages using HL7's Minimal Lower Level Protocol.
